{"tid":883642,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"怎樣叫兔子回到籠裡？不用抱！🐰🌟","createTime":"2018-10-31T04:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:08.000Z","uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"10b7df88f4c52f0c4bf27028106d9e61b67c008e","tid":883642,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal), 在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animals)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚。因此，兔子不喜歡被抱來抱去。當牠逃跑的時候，你還去追住抱，會令兔子和主人的信任更差。但如果主人與兔子的關係親密，牠都會喜歡同主人擁抱。以下video可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpyL0yEs-ka8&d=8px2%2Fe9R3OJ8fqB58kdGNI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d97ba0c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<br />\n最好的方法去叫牠入籠是每晚(比如：22:00）搖零食樽或pellet 樽幾下，再引牠進入籠吃。幾天後，兔子就會記得零食樽的聲音知道是時候回到籠吃。習慣後，牠會自動22:00左右提主人你是時候回到籠裡吃東西。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 有教：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RJcvi7o4YXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRJcvi7o4YXA&d=8px2%2Fe9R3OJ8fqB58kdGNI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b976d53b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RJcvi7o4YXA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兔子深入資訊：</span><a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=8px2%2Fe9R3OJ8fqB58kdGNI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fa3d114b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a></strong>"},{"pid":"204be7f64fb04b56b2cff18eb83a837d3700969e","tid":883642,"uid":46943,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:49:48.000Z","msg":"怎麼可以紅燒兔兔頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04ff1f61addd9167a659f926683cea5b746d11b","tid":883642,"uid":91633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}